Instructions to run the code :-

1. For the Q3a part, the name of the code file is Q3a.cpp. Simply run using the command 
	g++ Q3a.cpp && ./a.out
   The output of this code is given is Q3aPlain.txt		
   
2. For the Q3b part, the name of the code file is Q3b.cpp. Simply run using the command 
	g++ Q3b.cpp && ./a.out
   The output of this code is given is Q3bPlain.txt		